highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Top Songs Malaysia. “Golden” is the highest at #1.
“Night Changes” by One Direction has been on Top Songs Malaysia the longest, at 1692 days straight.
“Kasihnya Laila” by Jinbara is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Malaysia, up 81 spots at #108.
“Saya Anak Malaysia” by Dato David Aramugam, Nikki Palikat, Projector Band, Haoren, 蔡恩雨 Priscilla Abby, Meer Nash, Jenn Chia, and Jeryl Lee is the highest new entry on Top Songs Malaysia at #145.
